CQRS
----


Command - action indicates something should happen
Event - indicate something has happened


eg: user post a message

{ 'POST_MESSAGE', body:''}


REDUX
-----


Store, Actions, Reducers

Reducer - A function which specifies how the state changes in response to an action.
				It does not modifies the state, just return a new state.
Store - It is the responsibility of the store to modify the state.